<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      metal:use-macro="layout">
    <tal:block metal:fill-slot="main">
        <!-- Main hero unit for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
        <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Using Lemon Test</h1>
            <p>Lemon Test is a simple customer support testing tool.  It automatically runs a battery of tests on a customer support archive and reports actionable information for any known issues.</p>
            <p><a href="${request.route_url('upload')}">Click here to submit an archive.</a></p>
        </div>
    </tal:block>
</html>
